Binary: libyaz5, yaz, yaz-doc, libyaz-dev, yaz-illclient, yaz-icu

Description: Z39.50/SRW/SRU toolkit YAZ is a toolkit for the development of client and server software built around the ANSI Z39.50 (ISO 23950) standard for information retrieval. . YAZ supports Z39.50-2003 (version 3), SRU versions 1.1 to 2.0, and the industry standard ZOOM API for Z39.50.
